snippet.title: Planet Zoo trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description:
Planet Zoo is a new sim from the makers of Planet Coaster. As you can probably guess, this time you're managing a zoo full of realistic animals. It's up to you to care for them, so don't be a monster. Planet Zoo launches on November 5.

Read more here: https://www.pcgamer.com/planet-zoo-release-date-and-gameplay-revealed-at-the-pc-gaming-show/
